    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just don't see the point. the people i looked up to, the people who relied on my work... they deserved the truth, but i just gave them a fantasy for a decade. the version of me that existed in that lab doesn't actually exist. i'm just an empty shell now. everything is just quiet and dark.",
